    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor, age-appropriate wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is tidy and comfortable, though you might notice some slight creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that delivers a great balance of quality and value.",
