    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine currently has a significant knock and requires a major overhaul, and the transmission is slipping noticeably during gear changes. Externally, there is visible rust on the wheel arches and several large dents on the passenger side, while the interior shows heavy wear and multiple tears in the upholstery. This would be best suited as a donor vehicle for parts or a comprehensive restoration project for an experienced mechanic.",
