    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, having been maintained to the highest standards of excellence. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of care that borders on the fastidious. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of the marque.",
      "price": 44900.0,
